divs: Sighting DetailsThe two starlike objects are Venus and Jupiter vertically close to each other, Dec 1, we should see a patial crescent moon near the two planets. I believe this will not happen again until 2052. They are in the SW sky. I read about it on the internet. It was to begin Thanksgiving evening and go into next week.
Summary: Jupiter & Venus will be vertical to each other, crescent moon will come soon.
